<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<StringTableFile xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
  <Name>conversations\00_stronghold\00_recruits\00_cv_forge_skilltrainer_nikostas</Name>
  <NextEntryID>1</NextEntryID>
  <EntryCount>8</EntryCount>
  <Entries>
    <Entry>
      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Fatebinder." He gives you a quick bow. "I am Nikostas. I am not yet a master, but I find teaching others my ways only betters my own understanding. If you wish to be trained, only ask."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>4</ID>
      <DefaultText>"You may think we [url=glossary:forge-bound]Forge-Bound[/url] are simply tools of war, no different than hammers to shape metal." He smirks. "But it takes more than brawn to be effective on the battlefield. I am to become a master of many elements in my lifetime. If you wish to learn from me, you may ask."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>6</ID>
      <DefaultText>"I'd like to train."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>7</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Leave.]</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>8</ID>
      <DefaultText>"A strong blade at your side isn't the only implement of war at your disposal." He holds out his arm again, and instantly it becomes engulfed in a field of electricity. "I've devoted my life to understanding the elements and I only grow in that knowledge by teaching others. Ask, and I shall train you."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>9</ID>
      <DefaultText>"I do not have the implements to train while the forge is under maintenance. Check back once it has finished."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>10</ID>
      <DefaultText>The [url=glossary:forge-bound]Forge-Bound[/url] levitates a small glowing orb of flame in his hand before suddenly clenching it with his fist, smothering the flame into nothing but smoke and ash.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>11</ID>
      <DefaultText>"You look like you could use some training." </DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
  </Entries>
</StringTableFile>